= & \left(f'\left(g\left(x,y\right)\right)\cdot\frac{\partial g}{\partial x}\left(x,y\right),f'\left(g\left(x,y\right)\right)\cdot\frac{\partial g}{\partial y}\left(x,y\right)\right)\\
= & f'\left(g\left(x,y\right)\right)\cdot\nabla g\left(x,y\right)\\
